title: Sid Meiers Civilization II
description:
Sid Meiers Civilization II is a turn-based strategy computer game by Firaxis Games. Here you enter a world as civilizations are beginning to bloom. Play single player or against your friends and research technologies while you build cities & armies. Conquer your enemies or make allies and race to the pinnacle of civilization with pre-set victory conditions such as total conquest, the most Wonders of the World, win the space race and more!
